<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>💖 Date Invitation 💖</title>

<link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/canvas-confetti@1.9.3/dist/confetti.browser.min.js"></script>

</head>

<body>

<div class="hearts"></div>

<div class="container">

<div id="page1" class="card">

<h1>💖 Sweety 💖</h1>

<h2>Will you go on a date with me?</h2>

<p>
Made with ❤️ by
<br>
<b>Mehedi Hasan Tusar</b>
</p>

<div class="buttons">

<button id="yesBtn">
YES ❤️
</button>

<button id="noBtn">
NO 🙈
</button>

</div>

</div>

<div id="page2" class="card hidden">

<h2>Select Date 📅</h2>

<input type="date" id="date">

<button onclick="nextPage(3)">
Next →
</button>

</div>

<div id="page3" class="card hidden">

<h2>Select Time ⏰</h2>

<input type="time" id="time">

<button onclick="nextPage(4)">
Next →
</button>

</div>

<div id="page4" class="card hidden">

<h2>Choose Restaurant 🍽️</h2>

<select id="restaurant">

<option>Lapino</option>

<option>Deshi Bhoj</option>

<option>Pizza Times</option>

</select>

<button onclick="nextPage(5)">
Next →
</button>

</div>

<div id="page5" class="card hidden">

<h2>Choose Foods 🍕</h2>

<label>
<input type="checkbox" id="ice">
🍨 Ice Cream (Required)
</label>

<label>
<input type="checkbox">
🍕 Pizza
</label>

<label>
<input type="checkbox">
🍔 Burger
</label>

<label>
<input type="checkbox">
🍝 Pasta
</label>

<label>
<input type="checkbox">
🍗 Fried Chicken
</label>

<label>
<input type="checkbox">
🥤 Cold Coffee
</label>

<button id="finish">
Finish ❤️
</button>

</div>

<div id="page6" class="card hidden">

<h1>🎉 YAY!! 🎉</h1>

<h2>Thank You Sweety ❤️</h2>

<p>

I promise this will be
one of the sweetest memories
of our lives.

Thank you for saying YES.

See You Soon ❤️

</p>

</div>

</div>

<script src="script.js"></script>

</body>
</html>
